snippet.title: I Made My Racing Game Feel More Smooth
snippet.description:
Wishlist Apex Rush on Steam! - https://store.steampowered.com/app/2638250/Apex_Rush/
Follow the development of my game here: https://discord.gg/VEMAZeD
Today I'm back with another game making video, I made a lot of upgrades to my track racing game and it now feels 10x better! Watching a ton of tutorials for Unreal Engine 5 and Blender, the game now feels really good.

The plan is now to work on this level and make a prototype version for you all to try! So I have some work to do... 

I hope you all enjoy this video, Drop a LIKE & Subscribe if you're new! 

My Clothing Brand: https://nosleep.co/
